                        <interp inst="t18751025-604-verdict-1" type="verdictSubcategory" value="no_subcategory"></interp>GUILTY</rs>
                  </hi>.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Cooper was further charge with having been before convicted.</hi>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
